REFERENCE           10LAC001
LANG_ENGLISH        "Kyle Katarn?"

REFERENCE           10KJO001
LANG_ENGLISH        "Lando?  What are you doing here?"

REFERENCE           10LAC002
LANG_ENGLISH        "What does it look like I'm doing?  I'm sitting in a cell.  What about you?"

REFERENCE           10KJO002
LANG_ENGLISH        "I'm looking for Reelo Baruk."

REFERENCE           10LAC003
LANG_ENGLISH        "You too?  What's the Republic want with him?"

REFERENCE           10KJO003
LANG_ENGLISH        "A ship of his was involved in an...incident...on Artus Prime.  Remnant stuff."

REFERENCE           10LAC004
LANG_ENGLISH        "The Remnant?  Blast!  Now it's starting to make sense..."

REFERENCE           10KJO004
LANG_ENGLISH        "What?"

REFERENCE           10LAC005
LANG_ENGLISH        "Over the past few weeks, a mineral smuggling ring has infiltrated the Cloud City on Bespin.  Real slick group, too: they commandeered half of our loading platforms and Carbonite Chambers before we knew what hit us.  No one knows who's behind it, but it's become obvious that Reelo's garbage haulers are handling the transports.  I came down here to find Reelo, and persuade him to hand over the names of his employers."

REFERENCE           10KJO005
LANG_ENGLISH        "'Persuade'?"

REFERENCE           10LAC006
LANG_ENGLISH        "Hey, I can be a charming guy when I want to.  After a few bar fights and card games, I hadn't gotten any closer to Reelo, but I had begun to hear about a Remnant bigwig named 'Desann'... then I was captured."

REFERENCE           10KJO006
LANG_ENGLISH        "Desann?"

REFERENCE           10LAC007
LANG_ENGLISH        "You know him?"

REFERENCE           10KJO007
LANG_ENGLISH        "He's a Dark Jedi.  He and the Remnant have been performing sick experiments on New Republic citizens...among other things."

REFERENCE           10LAC008
LANG_ENGLISH        "Like I said, the Remnant connection makes sense.  These smugglers are much more organized than the kind of scum we usually get on Bespin; they've gotta be Imperials."

REFERENCE           10KJO008
LANG_ENGLISH        "Want me to get you out of here?"

REFERENCE           10LAC009A
LANG_ENGLISH        "If it's not too much trouble.  You'll need the password to get into Reelo's command center and open the cells."

REFERENCE           10KJO009
LANG_ENGLISH        "I'll be right back."

REFERENCE           10LAC010
LANG_ENGLISH        "I'm not going anywhere."

REFERENCE           10KJO028
LANG_ENGLISH        "Any idea what that might be?"

REFERENCE           10LAC016
LANG_ENGLISH        "Yeah. It's Ruby Bliels"

REFERENCE           10KJO031
LANG_ENGLISH        "I could go for one of those"

REFERENCE           10LAC021
LANG_ENGLISH        "Yeah, me too"

REFERENCE           10REE001
LANG_ENGLISH        "Looking for something?"

REFERENCE           10KJO010
LANG_ENGLISH        "Not anymore.  You're Reelo Baruk?"

REFERENCE           10REE002
LANG_ENGLISH        "In the flesh.  But who are you?"

REFERENCE           10KJO011
LANG_ENGLISH        "Does it matter?"

REFERENCE           10REE003
LANG_ENGLISH        "Not really.  Any last words?"

REFERENCE           10KJO012
LANG_ENGLISH        "What's a respectable gangster like you doing mixed up with a Remnant slime like Desann?"

REFERENCE           10REE004
LANG_ENGLISH        "Making money, of course.  Yah-hah-hah-haaaaa!"

REFERENCE           10LAC011
LANG_ENGLISH        "What went on up there?"

REFERENCE           10KJO013
LANG_ENGLISH        "I ran into Reelo."

REFERENCE           10LAC012
LANG_ENGLISH        "Did he tell you anything about the smuggling ring?"

REFERENCE           10KJO014
LANG_ENGLISH        "We didn't talk much."

REFERENCE           10LAC013
LANG_ENGLISH        "I see.  Listen, we'd better get out of here.  My ship's hidden nearby.  What about yours?"

REFERENCE           10KJO015
LANG_ENGLISH        "Reelo's thugs have probably already stripped it for parts by now."

REFERENCE           10LAC014
LANG_ENGLISH        "What about Jan?"

REFERENCE           10KJO016
LANG_ENGLISH        "Jan's...not with me on this one."

REFERENCE           10LAC015
LANG_ENGLISH        "You two've had another one of your fights, haven't you?  Well, c'mon, let's go.  You can buy her some flowers on Bespin."

REFERENCE           10KJO017
LANG_ENGLISH        "Pfew. What's that smell?"

REFERENCE           10KJO018
LANG_ENGLISH        "Reelo sure has a lot of heavy firepower to guard a bunch of 'trash'."

REFERENCE           10KJO019
LANG_ENGLISH        "Surveillance cameras. Reelo doesn't want to miss a thing."

REFERENCE           10KJO020
LANG_ENGLISH        "Where's Reelo? How could a Rodian that big just disappear?"

REFERENCE           10KJO021
LANG_ENGLISH        "I can't leave without Lando."

